{"title":"热土","authors":["刘高贵"],"dates":[{"year":1992,"month":3,"day":9}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"热土"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刘高贵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"依山傍水也依傍着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"花一样香酒一样醇的乡俗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大门朝南开"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小门也朝南开"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让阳光和山风"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"旁观我们的贫穷和富足"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一辈又一辈　用屋后的竹子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"编织粮囤　砍池塘边的老柳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"制作犁耧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"锄头明亮了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"道路就平坦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手心的茧子厚了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"庄稼穗就稠"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在季节的沟沟坎坎"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"点种些葵花和大豆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在最艰难的关口"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也不回头"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高声大嗓地吼一声民歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——亲人哪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"醉　是这一方热土"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"醒　是这一方热土"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}